item.text: Check the boxes to all that apply:
Do you speak any additional language(s) fluently (similar to a native speaker)?
What is your date of birth?
Do you have any of these conditions, diagnosed by a clinician? (Check all that apply if you currently have the condition) Voice Disorders
Can you use a smart device?
Do you have access to a smart device on a regular basis?

I want my contact information to be kept in a repository for this study which can be used to contact me to ask me to enroll in further studies or return important results. My information will not be shared with third parties.
Please review your answers reading all the way through the bottom and select an option. If you have any questions, you can still proceed with enrollment and ask or make changes at a later time.
Please select a reason for declining
